sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Usuario
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant SEC as JWT/Auth
    participant DB as MySQL

    U->>FE: Login
    FE->>API: POST /api/auth/signin
    API->>DB: Valida usuario
    API->>SEC: Genera JWT
    API-->>FE: Session + token
    FE->>API: Requests autenticados (Bearer)
    API->>SEC: Verifica token
    API->>DB: Lee/escribe datos
    API-->>FE: Respuesta
